OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police's longest-ever-
OL,8,Fserving police officer has said
OL,9,Fofficers are too often criticised as
OL,10,F"narrow-minded", as she celebrated her
OL,11,F50th year of service on the force.
OL,13,FPc Karen Giles, 68, who joined the Met
OL,14,Fin 1976, said the misconception that
OL,15,Fpolice officers are intolerant and
OL,16,F"set in their ways" is untrue, adding
OL,17,Fthat their work is frequently
OL,18,F"undersold".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@OO]xD@AOUxD@SO]zD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FSpeaking at a surprise party to
OL,8,Fcelebrate her decades-long service at
OL,9,FNew Scotland Yard on Tuesday, Pc Giles
OL,10,Fsaid: "I've never met people as broad-
OL,11,Fminded, as tolerant, and kind as the
OL,12,Fpeople I've met in the police service,
OL,13,Fboth police staff and police officers.
OL,15,F"People willing to put themselves at
OL,16,Frisk.
OL,18,F"People doing really kind things. Just
OL,19,Fdoing ordinary things on a daily basis
OL,20,Fto try and help people, and it goes
OL,21,Funrecognised."
OL,26,@rD@GOUwD@AOUzD@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FPc Giles, who has been a police
OL,8,Fconstable her whole career across
OL,9,Fvarious London boroughs, said officers
OL,10,Fof her rank are the force's "backbone".
OL,12,F"I love being a Pc. I've had a
OL,13,Fwonderful time as a Pc. I just think
OL,14,Fit's what keeps the Metropolitan
OL,15,FPolice and all the other police
OL,16,Fservices going," she said.
OL,18,F"Everybody makes a contribution, of
OL,19,Fcourse they do, but for me Pc's are
OL,20,Fthe backbone of the police service,"
OL,21,Fshe added.
OL,26,@rD@]OUrD@fO]tD@AOUxD@PO]zD@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FPc Giles also served in the Community
OL,8,FSafety Unit helping victims of
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse, which she described as
OL,10,Fher "favourite posting".
OL,12,FAsked about how policing has changed,
OL,13,FPc Giles said social media has made
OL,14,Fthe job increasingly "complicated",
OL,15,Falthough the basics largely remain the
OL,16,Fsame.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@WO]vD@VOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,F"We sort people's problems out. We
OL,8,Fdeal with domestics. We deal with
OL,9,Fpeople who take other people's
OL,10,Fproperty. It's basically the same,
OL,11,Fexcept obviously for online crime. But
OL,12,FI think the biggest change is
OL,13,Ftechnology," she said.
OL,15,F"Social media makes it very, very
OL,16,Fcomplex and difficult to deal with
OL,17,Fpeople.
OL,19,F"I think it's very difficult to get to
OL,20,Fthe truth of what's happening," she
OL,21,Fadded.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@LO]wD@AOU{D@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FPc Giles also said she never felt
OL,8,F"isolated" as a female police officer
OL,9,Fin the 1970s, adding that she has
OL,10,Falways felt able to deal with any
OL,11,Fincidents with male officers.
OL,13,F"There were a lot of women in my
OL,14,Fintake at Hendon Police College", she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@JO]uD@AOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,F"Out of 60 officers, 25 were women.
OL,8,FSo, actually, I didn't feel that there
OL,9,Fweren't many women because it was a
OL,10,Fsign of the times, if you like, and
OL,11,Fthere was a huge recruitment drive in
OL,12,F'76.
OL,14,F"It's ups and downs, you know. And
OL,15,FI've always felt able to deal with
OL,16,Fthings if there have been incidents.
OL,17,FIf people have ever said or done
OL,18,Fanything, I've taken it up with them."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FPc Giles, who is currently posted to
OL,8,FPlumstead, south-east London working
OL,9,Fin Integrated Offender Management, was
OL,10,Fsurprised with cake by her friends and
OL,11,Ffamily at the force's central London
OL,12,Fheadquarters.
OL,14,F"I really didn't have any idea at all.
OL,15,FIt's amazing. I'm just overwhelmed.
OL,16,FIt's lovely," she said.
OL,18,F"It seems a bit surreal when I think
OL,19,F50 years. I can't believe it's 50
OL,20,Fyears. It's you know, it's flown by."
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@MO]zD@AOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FHer daughter Jennifer Sharpling, 40,
OL,8,Fwho is also a serving police officer
OL,9,Fand helped organise the surprise, said
OL,10,Fher mother's decades-long service was
OL,11,F"unbelievable".
OL,13,F"They assumed that she would just
OL,14,Fleave the job when she was pregnant
OL,15,Fwith me... Women just didn't stay in
OL,16,Fthe job when they had children," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@NO]uD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,F"Even when things sort of get a bit
OL,8,Fhard, and they were for women when she
OL,9,Fjoined, and actually even up until
OL,10,Frelatively recently, and she just
OL,11,Falways kept going."
OL,13,FMs Sharpling added: "When you think
OL,14,Fwhen she started, she was walking
OL,15,Faround with a handbag, and that was it.
OL,17,F"And now you look at there are women
OL,18,Fin the job who are carrying tasers and
OL,19,Fdriving and doing all. So, the change
OL,20,Fhas been amazing."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]uD@UOUyD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FSheila Fellows-Turnbull, 70, from
OL,8,FHastings, East Sussex, who served
OL,9,Falongside Pc Giles in the late 1970s,
OL,10,Falso attended the surprise event.
OL,12,FMs Fellows-Turnbull, who served 30
OL,13,Fyears on the force, rising to the rank
OL,14,Fof detective sergeant, said Pc Giles
OL,15,Fhad always been "humble" about her
OL,16,Fsuccesses.
OL,18,F"She's done so much, and she is very
OL,19,Funderstated about it as well," Ms
OL,20,FFellows-Turnbull said.
OL,26,@wD@QOUwD@XO]zD@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,F"I find out things about her all the
OL,8,Ftime, bear in mind, we've been
OL,9,Falongside each other since the late
OL,10,F70s."
OL,12,FAssistant Commissioner Matt Twist, who
OL,13,Fis responsible for all borough
OL,14,Fpolicing in London, said Pc Giles's
OL,15,Fservice is "absolutely astonishing".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@EO]wD@LOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FSpeaking to Pc Giles as well as her
OL,8,Ffriends and family, he said: "I wanted
OL,9,Fto take today to one invite you here
OL,10,Fto say thank you for 50 years of
OL,11,Fservice, to say thank you in front of
OL,12,Fyour friends and family.
OL,14,F"And also, as you will know, over the
OL,15,Fyears we don't give away free cake or
OL,16,Ftea or anything else.
OL,18,F"But in so doing, to just put on you
OL,19,Fknow some cakes and to mark the
OL,20,Foccasion."
OL,26,@pD@^OUvD@AOUzD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784899120
OL,3,CMet Police's longest-ever-serving
OL,4,Cpolice officer celebrates 50 years of
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FAsked by Assistant Commissioner Matt
OL,8,FTwist about her plans for the future,
OL,9,FPc Giles said: "Keep coming to work!"
OL,11,F"As long as you keep coming, we'll
OL,12,Fkeep paying you," he replied.
